news.title: RR Kabel's net profit declines 33.16% in Q2 FY25
news.para: RR Kabel's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 1,817.35 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 11.88 per cent from Rs 1,624.43 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Kanodia Cement plans to launch IPO to raise around Rs 800 crore
news.para: Kanodia Cement, which currently has an annual capacity of around 5 million tonnes, is also looking to raise funds from institutional investors before filing the draft red herring prospectus (DRHP) with SEBI.

news.title: PNB Housing Finance's net profit increases by 22.63% in Q2 FY25
news.para: PNB Housing Finance's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 1,879.66 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 5.63 per cent from Rs 1,779.40 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Home First Finance's net profit up 24.12% in Q2 FY25
news.para: Home First Finance's net total income stood at Rs 374.23 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 34.62 per cent from Rs 277.98 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: China's Jiayuan to be delisted from Hong Kong stock exchange on October 29
news.para: Jiayuan was one of the first Chinese property developers ordered by the Hong Kong court to liquidate since the sector slipped into a debt crisis in 2021, resulting in many company defaults.

news.title: Existing home sales in US hit 14-year low in September 2024
news.para: The second straight monthly decline in home resales reinforced economists' views that the slump in residential investment, which includes homebuilding, deepened in the third quarter.

news.title: Citizens oppose PCMC’s proposal to change amenity land to residential in Tathawade
news.para: Federation members claimed the decision would set a trend for similar conversions and residents would lose space meant for public amenities.

news.title: Vietnam real estate tycoon's death row appeal to begin in November
news.para: Property developer Truong My Lan was found guilty in April of swindling cash from the Saigon Commercial Bank (SCB) -- which prosecutors said she controlled -- and sentenced to death in one of the biggest corruption cases in history.

news.title: ACC's net profit dips 48.52% in Q2 FY25
news.para: ACC's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 4,772.11 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 2.74 per cent from Rs 4,644.75 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Bilaspur: Forest department files case against five construction companies for dumping mud
news.para: The forest officers alleged that during the construction of four lanes, the companies unscientifically dumped soil on the land under the forest department, causing environmental and water pollution.

news.title: Kochi metro to begin construction of Vazhakkala station
news.para: Revenue authorities have issued land acquisition notification for the station on the upcoming Pink Line of KMRL connecting Palarivattom with Kakkanad Junction.

news.title: SIA field survey for Sabarimala Greenfield airport completed
news.para: The new independent agency conducted the survey after the earlier SIA conducted by the Centre for Management Development was cancelled following a court directive.

news.title: Kalyani Developers to invest Rs 4,500 crore over next two years in Bengaluru and Hyderabad
news.para: Kalyani Developers is also planning Rs 800 crore investment in two hotels comprising 300 rooms each in North Bengaluru. The company is also planning a mixed-use development in Hyderabad.

news.title: Goa mines department invites applications for sand extraction permits in Mandovi and Zuari rivers
news.para: The permissions will be issued in accordance with the eligibility criteria and other conditions under the Goa Minor Mineral Concession (Amendment) Rules, 2022.

news.title: Ajmer development body seals 39 illegal shops
news.para: Ajmer Municipal Corporation took action against a hotel and an under-construction building in the Delhi Gate area. AMC had also demolished encroachments on Kachari Road last Sunday.

news.title: Coimbatore councillors oppose 6% property tax hike from October 1
news.para: Coimbatore councillors also opposed the bid to award the contract for the maintenance of three crematoriums in the city to Isha Foundation.

news.title: Public hearing on proposed Ambuja cement plant held amid opposition by BRS in Telangana
news.para: A notification was issued for the public hearing a month ago as per procedures and people's views were taken today at the event, a senior official said.

news.title: Lucknow development body sanctions Rs 3.5 crore for facelift of multi-storey apartments
news.para: The announcement was made by LDA vice-chairman Prathamesh Kumar. A skating rink and a skateboarding bowl will also be constructed in the Lohia Park in Gomtinagar at a cost of Rs 1.3 crore.
